    "body": "I wanted to flag something I noticed while posting a few messages.\n\nIn the last few messages, I only tagged @Jake Feil  but the system automatically added the other Jake as well. I’ve had to manually remove Jake Harbaugh from the notifications each time.\n\nI’m not sure if this is related to the tagging logic, name matching, or the notification assignment, but I wanted to bring it up in case the system is auto-selecting both users because they share the same first name.\n\nCould you please take a look when you have a chance?\n\nThank you!",
