    "id": "399b0f44-281a-47d3-8b6f-740b77780b0f",
    "body": "I have another feedback item/question regarding the unread message notifications.\n\nI noticed that after opening and reading the messages inside the message section, the system still shows them as unread. For example, it may show “4 unread messages” on the main page even after I already opened and reviewed those messages.\n\nWhen I click back into the unread notification, it still shows them as unread unless I manually mark them as read. I just wanted to confirm if this is the intended behavior. Should messages only update as read when the user manually selects “Mark as Read,” or should they automatically update once the message has been opened/viewed?\n\nNot sure if this is working as designed, but I wanted to flag it because it may be helpful if the unread count refreshes automatically after the messages are viewed.",
